  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>

<% if false -%>
<img src="https://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/images/logo.gif"/>
<% end -%>

<p>Each new moon, the highest rated Voices of Humanity messages for the month are emailed to all active VoH subscribers. The Voice of Humanity-as-One is the overall highest rated message for the month. The Voice of Women is the highest rated message written by a woman and as rated by the women and similarly for the other Voices.</p>

<p>To block emails from the Voices of Humanity social media, <a href="https://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/optout?auth_token=<%= @cdata['recipient'].authentication_token %>">click here</a>.</p>

<hr/>


<div>
<%=raw @message %>
</div>

<hr style="clear:both">

<% if false %>
<img src="https://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/pixel/<%= @cdata['item'].id.to_i if @cdata['item'] %>_<%= @cdata['recipient'].id.to_i if @cdata['recipient'] %>.gif" width="0" height="0" border="0" style="display:none">
<% end %>

</body>
